{"tid":1631502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新文具：哨子","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:42:09.000Z","uid":26880,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4059b81de4c60345f06e6a5ba7fb79638bdb5887","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"每次和理非發夢都有同一情況發生，<br />\n就係指示傳得勁快，之後就傳錯哂。<br />\n例如要物資，但係又唔知邊度要，<br />\n叫人企散啲，就變咗向後走，<br />\n到真係要跑，又跑到亂哂，差啲人踩人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以用哨子傳遞指令？<br />\n例如吹兩下長就係企散啲，<br />\n兩下短就係向後走，<br />\n再做文宣同大家講，<br />\n等大家可以行動一致啲，<br />\n唔好咁易落單。<br />\n<br />\n利申：無做過童軍之類，唔知有冇吹哨子嘅公式，<br />\n如果有嘅可唔可以提供下資訊？"},{"pid":"9ef17aeb529c88d2933c40c827120b49210dc7d9","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f7ae56bcb21a6e1eda148ee39bdf9e4a1d9f5ab","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1af3312d0d2b955cb00d36c2e3ce398798f3e3c","tid":1631502,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b57ba4cde21b982a3e6df8fc1d9d7248b791be0","tid":1631502,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"一早有<br />\n救命用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a753cabf1b9b3dc861b6ef09f16579939da27b93","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b57ba4cde21b982a3e6df8fc1d9d7248b791be0","tid":1631502,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"一早有<br />\n救命用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"知道啊，係諗緊用途可唔可以廣泛啲"},{"pid":"c7197f54f877b1c3696bd7d36743b538ae9e5d5b","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad09f6c11d2035e01214de7f267c4d87390928b5","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3449a6b716d0811a2b383662e89b1ec93b92582b","tid":1631502,"uid":26880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a42ac966f6177f181abe6b29f586dc7c0db79b8","tid"